### Using REST Client Extension for Visual Studio Code

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/

### Get All Items
GET http://localhost:8080/items

### Get Item by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/items/1

### Create a New Item
POST http://localhost:8080/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 11,
  "name": "Item 11",
  "description": "A newly created item."
}

### Update an Existing Item
PUT http://localhost:8080/items/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Updated Item 1",
  "description": "An updated description for item 1."
}

### Delete an Item
DELETE http://localhost:8080/items/1